      <title>受可可价格上涨影响的巧克力制造商仍需重建对冲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/chocolate-companies-burned-by-cocoa-price-rally-still-need-to-rebuild-hedges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球巧克力制造商都在观望巧克力价格会跌到什么程度，然后再采取下一步行动，他们意识到自己可能已经错过了机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/chocolate-companies-burned-by-cocoa-price-rally-still-need-to-rebuild-hedges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 15:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
