      <title>欧盟强制荷兰采取财政路径以平衡预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/eu-to-force-fiscal-path-on-the-netherlands-to-balance-its-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将对荷兰实施更为严格的财政政策，迫使其进一步限制支出，此前这个传统上财政纪律严明的国家无视了欧盟执行机构的建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/eu-to-force-fiscal-path-on-the-netherlands-to-balance-its-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 14:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一轮警告，ZZZZ：华尔街对特朗普关税言论的反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/round-one-warning-shot-zzzz-wall-street-on-trump-tariff-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一晚，交易员们清楚地想起了候任总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 不靠谱的经济政策方针，当时他威胁要对美国三大贸易伙伴征收高额关税，以阻止毒品和移民流入美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/round-one-warning-shot-zzzz-wall-street-on-trump-tariff-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 14:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
