    <item>
      <title>交易员忽略特朗普的关税影响，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市创下历史新高，美元反弹，债券市场趋于稳定，投资者不再关注唐纳德·特朗普对美国主要贸易伙伴征收额外关税的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗撤回对 OPEC+ 石油生产政策的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/opec-has-little-room-to-revive-oil-supply-iran-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗驻 OPEC 代表表示，OPEC+ 几乎没有扭转石油减产举措的空间，减产举措已引发美国页岩油行业的一波竞争性供应，但该代表随后撤回了这一言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/opec-has-little-room-to-revive-oil-supply-iran-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 19:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
